{
  "title": "Savory Sweet Greek Seafood Horiatiki Pie",
  "description": "A buttery and chewy Greek dish featuring shortcrust pastry and seafood, perfect for a weeknight dinner. This pescatarian-friendly pie is a twist on the classic horiatiki salad.",
  "cuisine": "Greek",
  "diet": [
